            "CUSTOMER_PRODUCT_NCE_SUBSCRIPTION_CACEL_CONFIRMATION_TEXT": "<b style='color: #071437; font-size: 13.5px;'>Cancel subscription</b> <br/> <p style='color: #252f4a; font-size: 13.5px;'> Are you sure that you want to cancel {{productName}} ? </p><p style='text-align:left; font-size: 13.5px; color: #252f4a;'> To receive a refund, you must cancel subscriptions within 7 calendar days of purchase or renewal.<br/> <br><b style='color: #252f4a; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 18px;'> Please Note:</b><span style='color: #78829d; font-size: 13.5px;'> The customer will lose access to this subscription immediately upon cancellation and access can’t be restored after cancellation.  If you cancel the subscription within 7 calendar days, you'll be refunded for any time you've not used. A credit will appear in your next monthly invoice. <a target='_blank' href=\"{{cancelNewCommerceSubscriptionGuidLineURL}}\"> Learn more.</a></span> </p>",
